# PyInstaller
# WoW-WTF-Cleaner.spec — committed intentionally:
# it encodes --collect-all customtkinter + --collect-submodules,
# so anyone can reproduce the build with just:
#   pyinstaller WoW-WTF-Cleaner.spec
*.manifest
*.spec.bak

